OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FTwo women who were hospitalised after
OL,7,Fbotched bum and hip filler procedures
OL,8,Fin the back of a hair salon have
OL,9,Fjoined calls for proper regulation of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland's growing cosmetic
OL,11,Findustry.
OL,13,FBoth women developed severe bacterial
OL,14,Finfections after the non-surgical
OL,15,Fprocedures - which were carried out by
OL,16,Fthe same beautician who had no medical
OL,17,Fqualifications.
