OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FMelissa Crawford was left unable to
OL,7,Fwalk for weeks and is still physically
OL,8,Fand emotionally scarred after
OL,9,Fdeveloping complications from a BBL.
OL,11,FShe told UTV that at the time she was
OL,12,Funhappy with how she looked and had
OL,13,Fconsidered going to Turkey for the
OL,14,Fprocedure.
OL,16,FBut she then saw a local woman
OL,17,Fadvertising the procedure on social
OL,18,Fmedia and decided to book in with her
OL,19,F- a decision she now regrets.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
