OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FA few days after the procedure - which
OL,7,Fwas carried out in the back room of a
OL,8,Fhair salon by a beautician with no
OL,9,Fmedical qualifications - Melissa was
OL,10,Fhospitalised for seven days with a
OL,11,Fbacterial infection.
OL,13,FShe said doctors told her that she
OL,14,Fwould have probably died if she had
OL,15,Fshe not sought medical help when she
OL,16,Fdid.
