OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,F"They were really, really concerned
OL,7,Fand they said my infection markers
OL,8,Fwere really high, that I was
OL,9,Fborderline septic, and that they
OL,10,Fneeded to keep an eye on me and that I
OL,11,Fdefinitely needed surgery," she said.
OL,13,FShe added: "I never thought this would
OL,14,Fhappen to me. Like it's Northern
OL,15,FIreland, things like this don't happen.
OL,17,F"And then I was like, if I had died,
OL,18,Fwho would've looked after my children?"
