OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FMelissa underwent her procedure in May
OL,7,F2024. Seven months later, the same
OL,8,Fbeautician, who Melissa told about the
OL,9,Fmedical complications she had
OL,10,Fdeveloped, carried out a similar
OL,11,Fprocedure on another woman.
OL,13,FThe woman - who asked to remain
OL,14,Fanonymous - decided to have hip
OL,15,Ffillers as she did not like the shape
OL,16,Fof her body.
OL,18,FShe became unwell the following day
OL,19,Fand contacted the beautician for
OL,20,Fadvice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
