OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1740843953
OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FShe said the beautician gave her a box
OL,7,Fof antibiotics from Turkey.
OL,9,FA few days later she said she became
OL,10,Fso ill that she went to the Emergency
OL,11,FDepartment and was admitted to
OL,12,Fhospital with sepsis and cellulitis.
OL,14,FShe told UTV the doctor contacted the
OL,15,Fbeautician to ask who prescribed her
OL,16,Fthe filler she had used for the
OL,17,Fprocedure and the beautician said it
OL,18,Fwas from Turkey.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
