OL,3,CWomen hospitalised after botched back-
OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FBoth women have shared their
OL,7,Fexperiences as a warning to others
OL,8,Fabout the dangers of an unregulated
OL,9,Findustry.
OL,11,FThe Department of Health has told UTV
OL,12,Fthere are currently no plans to
OL,13,Fintroduce mandatory licensing for non-
OL,14,Fsurgical cosmetic procedures.
OL,16,FIt said that "any future review of
OL,17,Fregulation is contingent on available
OL,18,Fresources within the department".
