OL,4,Croom beauty procedure
OL,6,FIt added: "The risk to public safety
OL,7,Fposed by the unlawful distribution and
OL,8,Fmisuse of unauthorised medicinal
OL,9,Fproducts within the non-surgical
OL,10,Fcosmetic sector in NI is a serious
OL,11,Fissue.
OL,13,F"The department continues to take
OL,14,Fdecisive action to combat illegal
OL,15,Fpromotion, supply or misuse of
OL,16,Fmedicines and to alerting the public
OL,17,Fabout the dangers of using
OL,18,Funauthorised medicines outside of the
OL,19,Fregulated supply chain.
